snippet.title: Armor Critical Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Armor Critical is a free multiplayer online shooter, with a top-down 2D style.  Basically, players can join one of up to four teams of color-coded flying saucers to compete in various arenas and game modes. 


Play NOW: http://armorcritical.com
---
Twitter: http://twitter.com/armorcritical
